{"tid":754983,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"護理系正妹不怕走光　火車站救人讓網友一直看","createTime":"2018-07-25T00:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T01:05:19.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"717a2fd714e1c393659ecb70af8deec7dea4811d","tid":754983,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:05:23.000Z","msg":"中國遼寧省錦州醫科大學護理系1名正妹女學生丁慧，19日前往錦洲南火車站搭車，不料看見1名81歲老人家暈厥在地，不顧胸口走光風險，連忙上前救人，全程被民眾拍下貼網，讓網友直呼好美並不斷重複播放影片觀看。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php0dYf5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php0dYf5J.jpg&h=90c8fc3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國遼寧省錦州醫科大學護理系1名正妹女學生丁慧，19日前往錦洲南火車站搭車，不料看見1名81歲老人家暈厥在地，連忙上前施術救人，全程被民眾拍下貼網，讓網友直呼好美並不斷重複播放影片觀看。（圖擷取自影片）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phprE03As.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phprE03As.jpg&h=8de47072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n丁慧低調表示，當時聽見廣播，心裡毫無懸念，「我是學護理的，遇到這樣的事情就應該去幫忙」。（圖擷取自新華網）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpEflNTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpEflNTJ.jpg&h=95879cae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瀋陽鐵路局錦州南火車站對此事，發出致謝表揚信到丁慧就讀學校，校方才知悉學生的感人舉動。（圖擷取自新華網）<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，19日當天下午4點，81歲的男性長者與兒子下車後突然倒地不起，車站緊急廣播徵求有醫務經驗的民眾到場協助，錦州醫科大學護理系正妹女學生丁慧立刻前往，替老人家實施CPR維持心律，並在現場給予照護輔助直到救護車趕到，且當眾謝絕老人家屬給予的2000人民幣，約為台幣9012元。<br />\n<br />\n影片在網路上曝光後引發網友熱議，瀋陽鐵路局錦州南火車站對此事，發出致謝表揚信到丁慧就讀學校，校方才知悉學生的感人舉動，而後有媒體前往採訪，丁慧低調表示，當時聽見廣播，心裡毫無懸念，「我是學護理的，遇到這樣的事情就應該去幫忙」。<br />\n<br />\n受到救助的81歲長者兒子崔岱岱指出，父親到20日下午完全恢復意識後，第1個要求就是希望要找到救人的女學生並給予金錢作為謝禮，但當時已被婉拒，對於丁女的行徑感到無限謝意，崔男表示等到老父出院，「我一定親自登門道謝」；許多網友對此表示，「最美女大生無誤」、「我一直在看她CPR那段」、「救人也能這麼迷人」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2498039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2498039&d=%2B7Pt3pkRVvoFF7tiJgRHYJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=0bf3bc4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2498039&h=c16a037b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2498039</a>"},{"pid":"88572afb4869fb1ab047ac6b96c4db275bbd8081","tid":754983,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"想屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cb2b5a28aea1589cd4bd05d0e43bb8ed088504","tid":754983,"uid":96965,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"88572afb4869fb1ab047ac6b96c4db275bbd8081","tid":754983,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"想屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:27:11.000Z","msg":"放過阿伯啦"},{"pid":"76ca0d7ab8e0f746402f7dabf1dca4df2f055f72","tid":754983,"uid":42364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:31:16.000Z","msg":"呼吸脈膊都未度就去搓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p